dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Pacheco Pass quadrangle, Merced and Santa Clara counties, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Pacheco Pass, CA 1955. Photorevised 1971. AMS 1758 II SW--Series V895."
Includes location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology, most recent 1973.
